"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-04-parisolympics-kishane-thompson-mines-silver-olympic-mens-100m\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"KINGSTON, Jamaica- Kishane Thompson delivered a silver medal as he ran 9.79 seconds (1.m/s), the same time as winner Noah Lyles of the USA in the final of the men's 100m at the Olympics at Stade de France in Paris on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 35, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9678475830162435, \"rank\": 0.03322053707891014, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 208, \"end\": 213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997833865798, \"rank\": 2.1661345899337928e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the third medal won by Jamaica at the Olympics after triple jumper Shaneika Ricketts won a silver and shot putter Rajindra Campbell got a bronze on Saturday.\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999981348269443, \"rank\": 1.8640954938617077e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Ricketts\", \"score\": 0.9999999895403562, \"rank\": 1.0459683647712164e-08, \"text\": \"Ricketts\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Ricketts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Ricketts\"}, {\"begin\": 356, \"end\":